transforms.name: pinceau-transforms
transforms.result: footer{display:flex;min-height:var(--docus-footer-height);border-top-width:1px;border-top-style:solid;border-top-color:var(--elements-border-primary-static);padding:var(--docus-footer-padding);}footer .footer-container{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(12, minmax(0, 1fr));justify-items:center;gap:var(--space-2);}@media (min-width: 640px){footer .footer-container{justify-items:legacy;}}footer .footer-container :deep(.icon){width:var(--space-4);height:var(--space-4);}footer .footer-container a{color:var(--color-gray-500);}:root.dark footer .footer-container a{color:var(--color-gray-400);}footer .footer-container a:hover{color:var(--color-gray-700);}:root.dark footer .footer-container a:hover{color:var(--color-gray-200);}footer .footer-container .left{grid-column:span 12 / span 12;display:flex;padding-top:var(--space-4);padding-bottom:var(--space-4);order:1;}@media (min-width: 640px){footer .footer-container .left{grid-column:span 3 / span 3;order:0;}}footer .footer-container .left a{display:flex;align-items:center;}footer .footer-container .left p{font-size:var(--text-xs-fontSize);line-height:var(--text-xs-lineHeight);font-weight:var(--fontWeight-medium);}footer .footer-container .left-icon{flex-shrink:0;width:var(--space-4);height:var(--space-4);fill:currentcolor;margin-right:var(--space-2);}footer .footer-container .center{grid-column:span 12 / span 12;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;}@media (min-width: 640px){footer .footer-container .center{grid-column:span 6 / span 6;flex-direction:row;justify-content:center;}}footer .footer-container .center .text-link{padding:var(--space-2);font-size:var(--text-sm-fontSize);line-height:var(--text-sm-lineHeight);font-weight:var(--fontWeight-medium);}footer .footer-container .right{grid-column:span 12 / span 12;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:flex-end;}@media (min-width: 640px){footer .footer-container .right{grid-column:span 3 / span 3;margin-right:calc(0px - var(--space-4));}}footer .footer-container .right .icon-link{display:flex;padding:var(--space-4);}
